OL,3,CEight children killed in Louisiana
OL,4,Cmass shooting, US police say
OL,6,FA gunman killed eight children in
OL,7,Fdomestic-related shootings at
OL,8,Fdifferent homes in Louisiana before
OL,9,Fbeing killed during a pursuit by
OL,10,Fpolice officers.
OL,12,FShreveport police spokesperson Chris
OL,13,FBordelon said the victims ranged in
OL,14,Fage from one to about 14 years old. A
OL,15,Ftotal of 10 people were shot, he said.
OL,17,FThe gunman later died after a chase
OL,18,Fwith officers who fired at the
OL,19,Fsuspect, Bordelon said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
