OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776687067
OL,3,CEight children killed in Louisiana
OL,4,Cmass shooting, US police say
OL,6,FThe suspect stole a car while leaving
OL,7,Fthe scene of the shootings and was
OL,8,Ffollowed by police, according to
OL,9,FBordelon.
OL,11,FOfficials said they were still
OL,12,Fgathering details about the crime
OL,13,Fscene, which extended across three
OL,14,Flocations.
OL,16,FSome of the children shot were related
OL,17,Fto the suspect, Bordelon said.
OL,19,F"This is an extensive scene unlike
OL,20,Fanything most of us have ever seen,"
OL,21,FBordelon said.
