OL,3,CEight children killed in Louisiana
OL,4,Cmass shooting, US police say
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FAt a news conference outside the
OL,12,Fresidence where one of the shootings
OL,13,Foccurred, officials appeared stunned,
OL,14,Frequesting patience and prayers from
OL,15,Fthe community as they sorted through
OL,16,Fmultiple crime scenes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
