OL,3,CEight children killed in Louisiana
OL,4,Cmass shooting, US police say
OL,6,F"I just don't know what to say, my
OL,7,Fheart is just taken aback," Shreveport
OL,8,FPolice Chief Wayne Smith said. "I
OL,9,Fcannot begin to imagine how such an
OL,10,Fevent could occur."
OL,12,F"This is a tragic situation ` maybe
OL,13,Fthe worst tragic situation we've ever
OL,14,Fhad," said Tom Arceneaux, mayor of the
OL,15,Fcity in northwestern Louisiana with
OL,16,Fabout 180,000 residents. "It's a
OL,17,Fterrible morning."
OL,19,FLouisiana State Police say their
OL,20,Fdetectives have been asked by
OL,21,FShreveport police to investigate.
