OL,3,CEight children killed in Louisiana
OL,4,Cmass shooting, US police say
OL,6,FIn a statement, state police say no
OL,7,Fofficers were harmed in the shooting
OL,8,Fthat involved an officer after a
OL,9,Fpolice pursuit on Sunday morning.
OL,11,FState police are asking anyone with
OL,12,Fpictures, video or information to
OL,13,Fshare it with state police detectives.
